{"tid":380190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【雷霆一七】元朗淫竇重口味 4人妖serve客","createTime":"2017-08-30T02:30:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T16:43:02.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"37222bc5cb7271108293a1aab68f5894009cdc4e","tid":380190,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T02:30:02.000Z","msg":"【雷霆一七】元朗淫竇重口味 4人妖serve客<br />\n<br />\n【9:30】新增內容<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170830/large/1504046502_f75c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170830%2Flarge%2F1504046502_f75c.jpg&h=dd5222c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170830/large/1504046512_813d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170830%2Flarge%2F1504046512_813d.jpg&h=1e543540&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170830/large/1504046521_f53f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170830%2Flarge%2F1504046521_f53f.jpg&h=bef92d70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方凌晨在元朗進行聯合掃黃行動，在安寧路5至9號安榮樓，拘捕10多名泰國及內地女子，其中包括4名泰籍人妖，帶返警署調查。<br />\n<br />\n新界北總區重案組根據線報及經深入調查後，今日凌晨約零時展開一項代號「雷霆一七」的掃黃行動，突擊搜查多個位於元朗安寧路一帶的單位，共拘捕五名持護照外籍女子、七名持雙程證內地女子、四名持護照外籍男子(案中被捕人妖)，涉嫌「違反逗留條件」及一名三十六歲姓胡本地男子為「被通緝人士」。<br />\n<br />\n警員在行動中撿走大量寫有「新到美女」、「新到東歐美女」的廣告紙牌、毛巾、避孕套、漱口水及潤滑劑等。所有被捕人士現正被扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78438657460f7bb456152c9d8914c60f8aa748d7","tid":380190,"uid":25099,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T02:38:55.000Z","msg":"街邊有麗人 行前來「是否 想幫襯？」"},{"pid":"bdc8627e8a8594bd6e9f1518147fef4bd1b08a22","tid":380190,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-0